dct_title_s: Virginiae partis australis, et Floridae partis orientalis, interjacentiumq[ue] regionum nova descriptio
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Covers Atlantic Coast from Virginia to Florida. Signature: I, Catchword: tio. Prime meridian: [Ferro]. Bar scale above the neat line on the lower margin: Milliaria Germanica communia. From W.J. and J. Blaeu's Theatrum orbis terrarum. Includes decorative cartouche and coat of arms.
